  "design": {
    "name": "ua741",
    "source": {
      "kind": "hand"
    },
    "note": "uA741 (Gross/Roberts Ch.10) with DC-closed/AC-open feedback rig: Lf (1e9 H, 22->2) shorts at DC so the operating point is the linear closed-loop bias (output ~0 V); Cf (1e9 F, 2->0) grounds the inverting input at AC so the loop opens. tf(Vin,'22') is the open-loop gain in the plateau above the rig corner. Output node 22; supplies at 25(+15)/26(-15)."
  },
